description:
Minor amendment to planning permission LBI ref: P070059 dated 03/07/2007 to allow the:
a) Adjustment to the height of both Blocks A and B and the floor level of Block B;
b) Creation of a common room, laundry room and student accommodation management office with the northern wing of the existing Edwardian building;
c) Removal of common room, laundry room, electrical sub-station from the ground floor level of Block A; 
d) Creation of 2 new light wells to Block A; 
e) Extension of the first floor of Block B eastwards to meet with rear boundary of the Peel Centre (infilling the gap);
f) Creation of an additional student room at ground floor of Block A and additional student room at first floor of Block B, together with the rearrangement of internal layout of all student rooms in both Blocks;
g) Re-modelling of access ramps to Block A and Block B and creation of new ramps to the approach and within the northern access around the Edwardian building; 
h) Provision of new windows and rearranged windows to Block A and B and removal of brise soleils to Block B; and
i) Erection of a single storey refuse/recycling store to the north east of the northern wing of the existing Edwardian building and a single storey electrical sub-station adjacent to the vehicular entry to the site from Vernon Square.
